data.title: About: Joanne Samuel
data.meta_description: Joanne Samuel (born 5 August 1957) is an Australian film and television actress, who is best known for her role as the screen wife of Mel Gibson's title character in the 1979 film Mad Max.
data.text:
dbo:abstract

جوان صموئيل (بالإنجليزية: Joanne Samuel)‏ هي ممثلة أسترالية، ولدت في 5 أغسطس 1957 بسيدني في أستراليا. (ar)

Joanne Samuel (* 5. August 1957 in , New South Wales) ist eine australische Schauspielerin. (de)

Joanne Samuel (born 5 August 1957) is an Australian film and television actress, who is best known for her role as the screen wife of Mel Gibson's title character in the 1979 film Mad Max. (en)

Joanne Samuel (Sídney, 5 de agosto de 1957) es una actriz australiana de cine y televisión, que interpretó el papel de Jessie Rockatansky, esposa del personaje que realizaba Mel Gibson en la película de acción y ciencia ficción Mad Max de 1979.​ (es)

Joanne Samuel, née le 5 août 1957 à Sydney, est une actrice australienne connue pour avoir joué le rôle de la femme de Max (Mel Gibson) dans le film Mad Max. (fr)

조앤 새뮤얼(영어: Joanne Samuel, 1957년 8월 5일 ~ )은 오스트레일리아의 배우이다. 시드니 출신으로, 《매드 맥스》에서 주인공 맥스의 아내 제시 역으로 알려져 있다. (ko)

Joanne Samuel (Camperdown, 1957) è un'attrice australiana divenuta famosa per aver partecipato al film Interceptor con Mel Gibson. (it)

Joanne Samuel (ur. 5 sierpnia 1957 w Camperdown, Australia) – australijska aktorka filmowa i telewizyjna. (pl)
